      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I'd be happy to help you set up some E2E tests for your dashboard app. Here's a sample Playwright test suite that covers the login flow, main dashboard, and user profile page:\n\n```javascript\nconst playwright = require('playwright');\n\nconst test = async () => {\n  const browser = await playwright.chromium.launch();\n  const context = await browser.newContext();\n  const page = await context.newPage();\n\n  // Login flow\n  await page.goto('https://your-staging-app.com/login');\n  await page.fill('input[name=\"username\"]', 'your_username');\n  await page.fill('input[name=\"password\"]', 'your_password');\n  await page.click('button[type=\"submit\"]');\n\n  // Wait for login to complete\n  await page.waitForNavigation();\n\n  // Main dashboard\n  await page.goto('https://your-staging-app.com/dashboard');\n  await page.waitForSelector('h1.dashboard-title');\n  await page.waitForSelector('div.dashboard-content');\n\n  // User profile page\n  await page.goto('https://your-staging-app.com/profile');\n  await page.waitForSelector('h1.user-profile-title');\n  await page.waitForSelector('div.user-profile-content');\n\n  // Close the browser",
